    "body": "Another change we could implement at the same time would be linearising finalized blocks in the freezer database. Currently we key them by block root indefinitely, which leads to lots of non-sequential reads. Finalized blocks could be keyed by slot, which would make it quicker to replay them or serve them via BlocksByRange.",
